edu.nps.moves.gateway

Interface DISEndpoint

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DisNative, DisRedis, WebPageConnection

    public interface DISEndpoint
    interface for things that can read or send binary or JSON format DIS packets. This may be a web page connected via a web socket or, on the server side, a native socket that reads and writes bcast or mcast DIS.
